Package com.mygdx.gigabiteconomy.screens

Class TileManager

java.lang.Object
com.mygdx.gigabiteconomy.screens.TileManager
public class TileManager
extends java.lang.Object
Class to hold and manage Tiles. - Each MySprite instance is passed the TileManager it belongs to and sets a Tile to occupy - Then Player position can be retrieved from the Tile it's on (or the bottom leftmost if multiple -- Rat King)
